description: Welcome to The Residences at 527 East 7th Street, South Boston’s premier new boutique development. This stunning 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spans over 1,280 square feet and offers a perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and functionality. Enjoy deeded garage parking, a private roof deck, and private storage for added convenience. The open-concept living area features a cozy gas fireplace, while the chef’s kitchen is outfitted with Thermador appliances, Quartz countertops, and sleek modern finishes. Additional highlights include in-unit laundry, central A/C, and hardwood floors throughout. Thoughtfully designed for today's lifestyle, this home offers refined living in one of South Boston’s most desirable neighborhoods.

flooring: Top Floor Penthouse w/ Private Roof Deck
